### Description
Enhance the float-plan-api to accept an optional 'Food' field in the relevant endpoints, with a maximum length of 500 characters.

### Contract Changes
```json
{
  "paths": {
    "/float-plan": {
      "post": {
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "food",
            "in": "body",
            "description": "Optional food details",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "maxLength": 500
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "put": {
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "food",
            "in": "body",
            "description": "Optional food details update",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "maxLength": 500
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Acceptance Criteria
- The API must accept the 'Food' field in POST and PUT operations as an optional field with a max length of 500 characters.
- The API must handle cases where the 'Food' field is omitted gracefully.

### Relevant Registry Links
- [float-plan-api Repository](https://github.com/lackmannicholas/float_plan_api)
- Consumed by [float-plan](https://github.com/lackmannicholas/float_plan)
